So I choose this menu item here,
Inspect Element.

00:49:53.660 --> 00:49:58.730
And because I have a build of WebKit with
this additional feature in it,

00:49:58.820 --> 00:50:01.960
it'll appear any time
I click on anything.

00:50:02.010 --> 00:50:06.500
And immediately,
I get a view of the web page.

