00:51:33.580 --> 00:51:36.840
So if you have the inspector up
while you're loading the page,

00:51:36.890 --> 00:51:39.140
it'll also report any
errors in your HTML.

00:51:39.140 --> 00:51:43.740
And this page has some tags here,
has some examples here of some tags

00:51:43.770 --> 00:51:45.440
