The original HTML source,
which has this cool

00:52:31.420 --> 00:52:33.430
syntax highlighting here.

00:52:33.520 --> 00:52:35.780
The DOM,
which is the parsed version of the source

00:52:35.830 --> 00:52:37.750
with all the information we saw before.

