00:52:48.920 --> 00:52:51.670
It's real good when sleuthing and trying
to pick apart a site and figure out

00:52:51.690 --> 00:52:54.560
how it works or any kind of debugging.

00:52:54.560 --> 00:52:57.570
So the last thing I want to show
you here with the Web Inspector is

00:52:57.570 --> 00:53:01.600
this little view we have that
