00:53:13.940 --> 00:53:16.240
and then the scripts loading,
and then the images loading.

00:53:16.240 --> 00:53:19.230
And you can learn a lot about
why it takes a certain amount

00:53:19.240 --> 00:53:20.760
of time to load your site.

00:53:20.910 --> 00:53:27.430
This is really good for figuring out how
